n "News" General Manager of the Lagos State Emergency Management Agency (LASEMA), Mr. Adesina Tiamiyu on Thursday said the agency receives at least 100,000 calls daily from residents in the State via the emergency response number 767 and 112. September 27, 2018 In "Metro"